y |\\n| `eval/seeds/search_logs.csv` | lượt tìm found/sold_out |\\n| `eval/ground_truth.csv` | λ thật, uncensored demand, WTP params (NGOÀI DB) |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Kiến trúc script\\n\\n```\\nscripts/generate_seed_data.py\\n  ├── Phase 1: Catalog — stations, trains, seat_types, fare_classes\\n  ├── Phase 2: Calendar — calendar_features (2–3 năm)\\n  ├── Phase 3: Operational — trips, segments, seats, capacities, inventory\\n  ├── Phase 4: OD Products — lọc theo hub + threshold base_od\\n  ├── Phase 5: Simulation — demand → booking curve → transactions\\n  └── Phase 6: Export — JSON/CSV + ground_truth.csv\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Tham số chính (theo spec)\\n\\n- **Seed:** `RANDOM_SEED = 42`\\n- **Lịch sử:** 2 năm từ `2024-01-01` → `2025-12-31`\\n- **Tàu:** 1 tàu SE, 1 chuyến/ngày\\n- **K (quy mô):** tính ngược từ tải 0.65 × capacity ngày thường\\n- **NegBinomial r = 12**\\n- **WTP σ_log = 0.25, median = 1.15 × base_price**\\n- **Booking curve:** exp(−t/15), Tết thêm Gaussian tại t≈45\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Các điểm quan trọng cần xử lý đúng\\n\\n1. **Nút cổ chai Huế–Đà Nẵng:** pair_boost ×1.5 mọi OD đi qua\\n2. **OD mở bán:** chỉ ≥ 1 đầu hub hoặc base_od ≥ 0.5 khách/ngày\\n3. **Trừ inventory theo từng chặng OD đi qua** (dùng od_product_segments)\\n4. **Censored demand:** hết chỗ → sold_out log, không thành booking\\n5. **Browsing:** thêm 1.5–2× lượt found không mua\\n6. **Hủy vé:** 5–10% bookings\\n7. **Bất đối xứng Tết:** HN→SG trước Tết ×1.4, SG→HN sau Tết ×1.4\\n8. **ground_truth.csv ngoài DB** — λ thật, uncensored_demand, wtp_median, wtp_sigma\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phụ thuộc Python\\n\\nChỉ dùng stdlib + numpy + pandas (không cần thư viện nặng):\\n- `numpy` — NegBinom, LogNormal, random\\n- `pandas` — xuất CSV\\n- `json` — xuất JSON\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\nSau khi chạy, kiểm tra:\\n- Tải trung bình qua chặng Huế–ĐN ≈ 0.80 × capacity\\n- Tải ngày thường các chặng khác ≈ 0.65 × capacity\\n- Số OD active ~60–90/chuyến\\n- Tỉ lệ sold_out trong search_logs \u003e 0 (có censoring)\\n- Tỉ lệ cancelled trong bookings ≈ 5–10%\\n\",\"Description\":\"Implementation plan cho data generator\",\"Overwrite\":true,\"TargetFile\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\vando\\\\.gemini\\\\antigravity-ide\\\\brain\\\\2ec2195d-57da-406f-917b-25953f95f62e\\\\implementation_plan.md\",\"toolAction\":\"Creating implementation plan\",\"toolSummary\":\"Implementation plan\"}}]}"}
{"File":"c:\\Users\\vando\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\Hackathon-Viber-Code-Pro-Max\\docs\\ai-log\\sessions\\2026-07-17-gemini-2ec2195d.jsonl","LineNumber":32,"LineContent":"{\"step_index\":32,\"source\":\"MODEL\",\"type\":\"PLANNER_RESPONSE\",\"status\":\"DONE\",\"created_at\":\"2026-07-17T10:41:27Z\",\"content\":\"Tôi đã đọc xong spec và lập kế hoạch. Đây là những gì tôi sẽ làm:\\n\\n**Script:** `scripts/generate_seed_data.py`\\n\\n**6 phase:**\\n1. **Catalog** — 20 ga, 1 tàu SE, 2 loại chỗ, fare_class `standard`\\n2. **Calendar** — 2 năm `calendar_features` với lễ/Tết/mùa/thời tiết\\n3. **Operational** — trips (1/ngày) → segments (×19) → seats (×444) → capacities/inventory\\n4. **OD Products** — lọc ~60–90 OD/chuyến theo hub rule + base_od threshold\\n5. **Simulation** — vòng lặp: λ → NegBinomial → booking curve → WTP → booking/sold_out/browsing/cancellation\\n6. **Export** — 14 file CSV/JSON vào `eval/seeds/` + `eval/ground_truth.csv`\\n\\n**Điểm đặc biệt cần xử lý:**\\n- Nút cổ chai Huế–ĐN (pair_boost ×1.5)\\n- Bất đối xứng Tết (HN→SG trước Tết ×1.4, SG→HN sau Tết ×1.4)\\n- Trừ inventory theo **từng chặng** OD đi qua (censored demand đúng)\\n- ground_truth.csv **ngoài DB**\\n\\nBạn duyệt để tôi bắt đầu code không?\"}"}
{"File":"c:\\Users\\vando\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\Hackathon-Viber-Code-Pro-Max\\docs\\ai-log\\sessions\\2026-07-17-gemini-2ec2195d.jsonl","LineNumber":34,"LineContent":"{\"step_index\":34,\"source\":\"MODEL\",\"type\":\"PLANNER_RESPONSE\",\"status\":\"DONE\",\"created_at\":\"2026-07-17T10:42:02Z\",\"content\":\"Bắt đầu viết script ngay!\",\"thinking\":\"The user has approved the plan. Let me now write the actual data generator script. This is a complex script that needs to follow all the rules in the spec. Let me write it carefully.\\n\\nKey things to implement:\\n1. 20 stations with km distances\\n2. 1 SE train, daily for 2 years (2024-01-01 to 2025-12-31)\\n3. 2 seat types: ngoi_mem (192 cap), giuong_nam_k6 (252 cap)\\n4. 19 segments between stations\\n5. Calendar features with holidays/Tet/seasons\\n6. OD products filtered by hub rule\\n7. Demand simulation with NegBinomial, booking curve, WTP\\n8. Export to CSV/JSON\\n\\nNow I'll write the script to generate all this data.\",\"tool_calls\":[{\"name\":\"write_to_file\",\"args\":{\"CodeContent\":\"\\\"\\\"\\\"\\ngenerate_seed_data.py — Bộ sinh dữ liệu mô phỏng SRRM MVP\\nTheo luật: Luat_Sinh_Du_Lieu_SRRM.md\\nChạy: python scripts/generate_seed_data.py\\nĐầu ra: eval/seeds/*.csv, eval/seeds/*.json, eval/ground_truth.csv\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport csv\\nimport json\\nimport math\\nimport os\\nimport random\\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\\nfrom datetime import date, datetime, timedelta\\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Optional, Tuple\\n\\nimport numpy as np\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 0. Cấu hình chung\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\nRANDOM_SEED = 42\\nrng = np.random.default_rng(RANDOM_SEED)\\nrandom.seed(RANDOM_SEED)\\n\\nROOT = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))\\nSEEDS_DIR = os.path.join(ROOT, \\\"eval\\\", \\\"seeds\\\")\\nEVAL_DIR = os.path.join(ROOT, \\\"eval\\\")\\nos.makedirs(SEEDS_DIR, exist_ok=True)\\nos.makedirs(EVAL_DIR, exist_ok=True)\\n\\nSIM_START = date(2024, 1, 1)\\nSIM_END = date(2025, 12, 31)\\n\\n# Số ngày trước chuyến mà cửa sổ đặt vé mở\\nBOOKING_WINDOW = 60\\n\\n# NegBinomial r (over-dispersion); r=12 → nhiễu nhẹ, dễ học\\nNEGBINOM_R = 12\\n\\n# WTP LogNormal: median = WTP_MEDIAN_RATIO × base_price, σ_log = WTP_SIGMA\\nWTP_MEDIAN_RATIO = 1.15\\nWTP_SIGMA = 0.25\\n\\n# Hằng số giá\\nFIXED_FEE = 20_000          # đồng\\nPRICE_PER_KM = {\\\"ngoi_mem\\\": 670, \\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\": 760}\\n\\n# Tỉ lệ hủy vé\\nCANCEL_RATE = 0.07\\n\\n# Hệ số browsing (lượt found không mua, thêm ngoài lượt đến thật)\\nBROWSE_MULTIPLIER = 1.7\\n\\n# Tỉ lệ seat_share theo khoảng cách (ngắn→ngoi_mem, dài→giuong_nam_k6)\\n# threshold 400 km\\nSHORT_HAUL_SHARES = {\\\"ngoi_mem\\\": 0.70, \\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\": 0.30}\\nLONG_HAUL_SHARES  = {\\\"ngoi_mem\\\": 0.35, \\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\": 0.65}\\nDISTANCE_THRESHOLD_KM = 400\\n\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 1. Catalog cố định\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\nSTATIONS = [\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 1,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"HAN\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Hà Nội\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 0,    \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 1.00, \\\"display_order\\\": 1},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 2,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"PHL\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Phủ Lý\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 56,   \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.25, \\\"display_order\\\": 2},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 3,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"NDI\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Nam Định\\\",                  \\\"km\\\": 87,   \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.40, \\\"display_order\\\": 3},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 4,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"NBH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Ninh Bình\\\",                 \\\"km\\\": 115,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.30, \\\"display_order\\\": 4},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 5,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"THH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Thanh Hóa\\\",                 \\\"km\\\": 175,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.50, \\\"display_order\\\": 5},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 6,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"VIH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Vinh\\\",                      \\\"km\\\": 319,  \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 0.50, \\\"display_order\\\": 6},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 7,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"DHO\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Đồng Hới\\\",                  \\\"km\\\": 522,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.30, \\\"display_order\\\": 7},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 8,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"DHA\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Đông Hà\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 622,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.25, \\\"display_order\\\": 8},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 9,  \\\"code\\\": \\\"HUE\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Huế\\\",                       \\\"km\\\": 688,  \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 0.60, \\\"display_order\\\": 9},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 10, \\\"code\\\": \\\"DAN\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Đà Nẵng\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 791,  \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 0.90, \\\"display_order\\\": 10},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 11, \\\"code\\\": \\\"TAK\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Tam Kỳ\\\",                    \\\"km\\\": 865,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.35, \\\"display_order\\\": 11},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 12, \\\"code\\\": \\\"QNG\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Quảng Ngãi\\\",                \\\"km\\\": 928,  \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.35, \\\"display_order\\\": 12},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 13, \\\"code\\\": \\\"DTR\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Diêu Trì (Quy Nhơn)\\\",       \\\"km\\\": 1096, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.45, \\\"display_order\\\": 13},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 14, \\\"code\\\": \\\"TYH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Tuy Hòa\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 1198, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.30, \\\"display_order\\\": 14},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 15, \\\"code\\\": \\\"NTG\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Nha Trang\\\",                 \\\"km\\\": 1315, \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 0.70, \\\"display_order\\\": 15},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 16, \\\"code\\\": \\\"TPC\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Tháp Chàm\\\",                 \\\"km\\\": 1408, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.25, \\\"display_order\\\": 16},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 17, \\\"code\\\": \\\"BTH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Bình Thuận (Mương Mán)\\\",    \\\"km\\\": 1551, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.30, \\\"display_order\\\": 17},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 18, \\\"code\\\": \\\"LKH\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Long Khánh\\\",                \\\"km\\\": 1637, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.20, \\\"display_order\\\": 18},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 19, \\\"code\\\": \\\"BHO\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Biên Hòa\\\",                  \\\"km\\\": 1694, \\\"is_hub\\\": False, \\\"pop\\\": 0.40, \\\"display_order\\\": 19},\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 20, \\\"code\\\": \\\"SGO\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Sài Gòn\\\",                   \\\"km\\\": 1726, \\\"is_hub\\\": True,  \\\"pop\\\": 1.00, \\\"display_order\\\": 20},\\n]\\nSTATION_BY_ID  = {s[\\\"id\\\"]: s for s in STATIONS}\\nSTATION_BY_CODE = {s[\\\"code\\\"]: s for s in STATIONS}\\nHUB_IDS = {s[\\\"id\\\"] for s in STATIONS if s[\\\"is_hub\\\"]}\\n\\nTRAINS = [\\n    {\\\"id\\\": 1, \\\"code\\\": \\\"SE1\\\", \\\"name\\\": \\\"Thống Nhất SE1\\\", \\\"is_active\\\": True},\\n]\\n\\nSEAT_TYPES = [\\n    {\\\"code\\\": \\\"ngoi_mem\\\",       \\\"name\\\": \\\"Ngồi mềm điều hòa\\\",   \\\"is_active\\\": True, \\\"capacity_per_trip\\\": 192},\\n    {\\\"code\\\": \\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\",  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Giường nằm khoang 6\\\", \\\"is_active\\\": True, \\\"capacity_per_trip\\\": 252},\\n]\\nSEAT_CAP = {st[\\\"code\\\"]: st[\\\"capacity_per_trip\\\"] for st in SEAT_TYPES}\\nSEAT_CONFIGS = {\\n    \\\"ngoi_mem\\\":       {\\\"coaches\\\": 3, \\\"per_coach\\\": 64},\\n    \\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\":  {\\\"coaches\\\": 6, \\\"per_coach\\\": 42},\\n}\\n\\nFARE_CLASSES = [\\n    {\\\"code\\\": \\\"standard\\\", \\\"name\\\": \\\"Phổ thông\\\", \\\"is_active\\\": True},\\n]\\n\\n# Lịch trình SE1 — giờ chạy tính từ HN (giờ thập phân)\\n# departure HN 22:20 → t=0 tham chiếu là 22:20 ngày service_date\\nDEPARTURE_BASE_HOUR = 22 + 20/60   # 22.333...\\nSTATION_HOUR_OFFSET = {\\n    \\\"HAN\\\": 0.0,\\n    \\\"PHL\\\": 0.75,\\n    \\\"NDI\\\": 1.25,\\n    \\\"NBH\\\": 1.75,\\n    \\\"THH\\\": 3.0,\\n    \\\"VIH\\\": 5 + 35/60,\\n    \\\"DHO\\\": 10.0,\\n    \\\"DHA\\\": 11.5,\\n    \\\"HUE\\\": 12 + 40/60,\\n    \\\"DAN\\\": 15 + 25/60,\\n    \\\"TAK\\\": 17.0,\\n    \\\"QNG\\\": 18.5,\\n    \\\"DTR\\\": 22.5,\\n    \\\"TYH\\\": 25.0,\\n    \\\"NTG\\\": 24 + 0/60,    # ~24h sau\\n    \\\"TPC\\\": 26.5,\\n    \\\"BTH\\\": 29.5,\\n    \\\"LKH\\\": 30.5,\\n    \\\"BHO\\\": 31.0,\\n    \\\"SGO\\\": 31 + 25/60,\\n}\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 2. Hàm tiện ích\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\ndef date_range(start: date, end: date):\\n    d = start\\n    while d \u003c= end:\\n        yield d\\n        d += timedelta(days=1)\\n\\n\\ndef to_iso(d: date, hour_offset: float = 0.0) -\u003e str:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Chuyển ngày + số giờ lẻ sang ISO 8601.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    dt = datetime(d.year, d.month, d.day, 22, 20)  # base departure\\n    dt += timedelta(hours=hour_offset)\\n    return dt.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\")\\n\\n\\ndef segment_distance(s_from: dict, s_to: dict) -\u003e float:\\n    return float(s_to[\\\"km\\\"] - s_from[\\\"km\\\"])\\n\\n\\ndef base_price(seat_type: str, distance_km: float) -\u003e int:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Tính base_price theo công thức spec, làm tròn đến 1000đ.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    price = FIXED_FEE + PRICE_PER_KM[seat_type] * distance_km\\n    return int(round(price / 1000) * 1000)\\n\\n\\ndef displayed_price(bp: int, lead_days: int, weekday: int, rng: np.random.Generator) -\u003e int:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Giá hiển thị biến thiên theo lead time, ngày tuần, nhiễu.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    factor = 1.0\\n    if lead_days \u003c 7:\\n        factor += 0.15\\n    if weekday in (4, 6):  # T6=4, CN=6 (Monday=0)\\n        factor += 0.10\\n    noise = rng.uniform(-0.15, 0.20)\\n    factor += noise\\n    return max(int(round(bp * factor / 1000) * 1000), 10_000)\\n\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 3. Calendar features\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\n# Ngày lễ cố định (tháng, ngày) — không tính năm\\nFIXED_HOLIDAYS = {\\n    (1, 1): \\\"Tết Dương lịch\\\",\\n    (4, 30): \\\"Ngày Giải phóng\\\",\\n    (5, 1): \\\"Quốc tế Lao động\\\",\\n    (9, 2): \\\"Quốc khánh\\\",\\n}\\n\\n# Tết Âm lịch (ngày dương tương đương, ±10 ngày xung quanh ngày mùng 1)\\nTET_LUNAR_NEW_YEAR = {\\n    2024: date(2024, 2, 10),\\n    2025: date(2025, 1, 29),\\n}\\nTET_WINDOW = 10  # ngày\\n\\n\\ndef build_calendar(start: date, end: date) -\u003e List[dict]:\\n    rows = []\\n    for d in date_range(start, end):\\n        is_holiday = False\\n        holiday_name = None\\n        for (m, dy), name in FIXED_HOLIDAYS.items():\\n            if d.month == m and d.day == dy:\\n                is_holiday = True\\n                holiday_name = name\\n\\n        is_tet = False\\n        for yr, tet_date in TET_LUNAR_NEW_YEAR.items():\\n            if abs((d - tet_date).days) \u003c= TET_WINDOW:\\n                is_tet = True\\n\\n        # Mùa\\n        month = d.month\\n        if month in (6, 7, 8):\\n            season = \\\"summer\\\"\\n        elif month in (12, 1, 2):\\n            season = \\\"winter\\\"\\n        elif month in (3, 4, 5):\\n            season = \\\"spring\\\"\\n        else:\\n            season = \\\"autumn\\\"\\n\\n        # Thời tiết (đơn giản hóa)\\n        if month in (10, 11, 12):\\n            weather = \\\"rainy_central\\\"\\n        elif month in (6, 7, 8):\\n            weather = \\\"hot_dry\\\"\\n        else:\\n            weather = \\\"mild\\\"\\n\\n        rows.append({\\n            \\\"service_date\\\": d.isoformat(),\\n            \\\"is_holiday\\\": is_holiday,\\n            \\\"is_tet\\\": is_tet,\\n            \\\"season\\\": season,\\n            \\\"weather\\\": weather,\\n            \\\"local_event\\\": holiday_name,\\n            \\\"created_at\\\": datetime.now().isoformat(),\\n            \\\"updated_at\\\": datetime.now().isoformat(),\\n        })\\n    return rows\\n\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 4. Demand model\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\n# f_dow: Monday=0 ... Sunday=6\\nF_DOW = {0: 0.85, 1: 0.80, 2: 0.85, 3: 1.10, 4: 1.45, 5: 1.20, 6: 1.50}\\n\\n# Du lịch hub (Đà Nẵng, Nha Trang)\\nTOURIST_HUB_IDS = {STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"DAN\\\"][\\\"id\\\"], STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"NTG\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]}\\nHUE_ID = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"HUE\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\nDAN_ID = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"DAN\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\n\\n# Chặng cổ chai Huế–Đà Nẵng (idx 8 trong danh sách chặng 0-indexed)\\nBOTTLENECK_PAIR = (HUE_ID, DAN_ID)\\n\\n\\ndef f_season(d: date, origin_id: int, dest_id: int) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Hệ số mùa.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    month = d.month\\n    is_tourist_od = (origin_id in TOURIST_HUB_IDS or dest_id in TOURIST_HUB_IDS)\\n    if month in (6, 7, 8) and is_tourist_od:\\n        return 1.35\\n    if month in (2, 3, 4):\\n        return 0.85\\n    return 1.0\\n\\n\\ndef f_holiday(d: date, origin_id: int, dest_id: int) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Hệ số ngày lễ / Tết kèm bất đối xứng chiều.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    # Tết\\n    for yr, tet_date in TET_LUNAR_NEW_YEAR.items():\\n        delta = (d - tet_date).days\\n        if -TET_WINDOW \u003c= delta \u003c= TET_WINDOW:\\n            base = 3.0\\n            han_id = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"HAN\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\n            sgo_id = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"SGO\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\n            # Trước Tết HN→SG: ×1.4\\n            if delta \u003c 0 and origin_id == han_id:\\n                return base * 1.4\\n            # Sau Tết SG→HN: ×1.4\\n            if delta \u003e 0 and origin_id == sgo_id:\\n                return base * 1.4\\n            return base\\n\\n    # Ngày lễ thông thường\\n    for (m, dy) in FIXED_HOLIDAYS:\\n        if d.month == m and d.day == dy:\\n            return 1.8\\n\\n    return 1.0\\n\\n\\ndef pair_boost(origin_id: int, dest_id: int, traverses_bottleneck: bool) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Boost riêng cho một số OD đặc biệt.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    han_id = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"HAN\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\n    vih_id = STATION_BY_CODE[\\\"VIH\\\"][\\\"id\\\"]\\n    # HN–Vinh (tuyến ngắn đông)\\n    if {origin_id, dest_id} == {han_id, vih_id}:\\n        return 1.6\\n    # Mọi OD qua Huế–ĐN\\n    if traverses_bottleneck:\\n        return 1.5\\n    return 1.0\\n\\n\\ndef seat_share(distance_km: float, seat_type: str) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Tỉ lệ nhu cầu theo loại chỗ dựa vào cự ly.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    if distance_km \u003c= DISTANCE_THRESHOLD_KM:\\n        return SHORT_HAUL_SHARES[seat_type]\\n    return LONG_HAUL_SHARES[seat_type]\\n\\n\\ndef compute_lambda(\\n    origin: dict, dest: dict, distance_km: float,\\n    seat_type: str, traverses_bottleneck: bool,\\n    d: date, K: float\\n) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Tính λ_od(d) theo công thức spec.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    base_od = (\\n        origin[\\\"pop\\\"] * dest[\\\"pop\\\"]\\n        * math.exp(-distance_km / 800)\\n        * pair_boost(origin[\\\"id\\\"], dest[\\\"id\\\"], traverses_bottleneck)\\n        * seat_share(distance_km, seat_type)\\n    )\\n    lam = (K * base_od\\n           * F_DOW[d.weekday()]\\n           * f_season(d, origin[\\\"id\\\"], dest[\\\"id\\\"])\\n           * f_holiday(d, origin[\\\"id\\\"], dest[\\\"id\\\"]))\\n    return max(lam, 0.0)\\n\\n\\ndef sample_demand(lam: float) -\u003e int:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"D ~ NegativeBinomial(mean=λ, r=12).\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    if lam \u003c= 0:\\n        return 0\\n    r = NEGBINOM_R\\n    p = r / (r + lam)\\n    return int(rng.negative_binomial(r, p))\\n\\n\\ndef booking_curve_weights(n_days: int, service_date: date) -\u003e np.ndarray:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Trải D khách qua T ngày trước ngày chạy.\\n    t=0 là ngày chạy, t=59 là 60 ngày trước.\\n    Tỉ lệ ∝ exp(−t/15); Tết thêm Gaussian tại t≈45.\\n    Trả về mảng weights [t=59..0] (gần ngày = index cuối).\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    t = np.arange(n_days, 0, -1)  # t=60,59,...,1\\n    weights = np.exp(-t / 15.0)\\n\\n    # Bướu Tết\\n    for yr, tet_date in TET_LUNAR_NEW_YEAR.items():\\n        if service_date.year == yr or (service_date.year == yr - 1 and service_date.month == 12):\\n            delta_tet = (tet_date - service_date).days\\n            if 0 \u003c delta_tet \u003c= 60:\\n                # Thêm Gaussian tại t≈45 (tức 45 ngày trước ngày chạy)\\n                gaussian_center = 45\\n                weights += 0.5 * np.exp(-((t - gaussian_center) ** 2) / (2 * 8 ** 2))\\n    weights = weights / weights.sum()\\n    return weights\\n\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 5. Tính K (calibration)\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\ndef calibrate_K(od_list: list, target_load: float = 0.65) -\u003e float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Chọn K sao cho tổng λ ngày thường (thứ 3) qua mỗi chặng ≈ target_load × capacity.\\n    Dùng ngày thứ 3 trung bình (không lễ, không Tết, không hè) làm baseline.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    ref_date = date(2024, 3, 19)  # Thứ 3, tháng 3 (thấp điểm)\\n\\n    # Tính tổng base_od × f_dow × f_season × f_holiday trên tất cả OD cho từng chặng\\n    # Dùng K=1 để calibrate\\n    segment_lambdas: Dict[int, float] = {}  # segment_idx -\u003e tổng lambda (K=1)\\n\\n    for od in od_list:\\n        origin = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"]]\\n        dest   = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"]]\\n        seat   = od[\\\"seat_type\\\"]\\n        dist   = od[\\\"distance_km\\\"]\\n        traverses = od[\\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\"]\\n\\n        lam_k1 = compute_lambda(origin, dest, dist, seat, traverses, ref_date, K=1.0)\\n        for seg_idx in od[\\\"segment_indices\\\"]:\\n            segment_lambdas[seg_idx] = segment_lambdas.get(seg_idx, 0.0) + lam_k1\\n\\n    if not segment_lambdas:\\n        return 1.0\\n\\n    avg_lambda_k1 = sum(segment_lambdas.values()) / len(segment_lambdas)\\n    avg_capacity  = (SEAT_CAP[\\\"ngoi_mem\\\"] + SEAT_CAP[\\\"giuong_nam_k6\\\"]) / 2\\n    target = target_load * avg_capacity\\n\\n    K = target / avg_lambda_k1 if avg_lambda_k1 \u003e 0 else 1.0\\n    return K\\n\\n\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n# 6. Sinh toàn bộ dữ liệu\\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\\n\\ndef main():\\n    print(\\\"=== SRRM Data Generator ===\\\")\\n    print(f\\\"Seed: {RANDOM_SEED}, Period: {SIM_START} → {SIM_END}\\\")\\n\\n    # ── Phase 1: Catalog ─────────────────────\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n[1/6] Catalog...\\\")\\n    _write_json(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"stations.json\\\", [\\n        {k: v for k, v in s.items() if k not in (\\\"km\\\", \\\"is_hub\\\", \\\"pop\\\")}\\n        for s in STATIONS\\n    ])\\n    _write_json(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"trains.json\\\", TRAINS)\\n    _write_json(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"seat_types.json\\\", [\\n        {k: v for k, v in st.items() if k != \\\"capacity_per_trip\\\"}\\n        for st in SEAT_TYPES\\n    ])\\n    _write_json(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"fare_classes.json\\\", FARE_CLASSES)\\n\\n    # ── Phase 2: Calendar ────────────────────\\n    print(\\\"[2/6] Calendar features...\\\")\\n    calendar_rows = build_calendar(SIM_START, SIM_END)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"calendar_features.csv\\\", calendar_rows)\\n    calendar_by_date = {r[\\\"service_date\\\"]: r for r in calendar_rows}\\n\\n    # ── Phase 3: Operational ─────────────────\\n    print(\\\"[3/6] Trips / Segments / Seats / Capacities / Inventory...\\\")\\n    sim_dates = list(date_range(SIM_START, SIM_END))\\n    n_days = len(sim_dates)\\n\\n    trips = []\\n    segments_all = []\\n    seats_all = []\\n    seg_capacities = []\\n    seg_inventory = []\\n\\n    trip_id = 1\\n    segment_id = 1\\n    seat_id = 1\\n\\n    # Lưu map: trip_id → {segment_seq: segment_id}\\n    trip_segment_map: Dict[int, Dict[int, int]] = {}  # trip_id -\u003e {seq_no: seg_id}\\n    trip_date_map: Dict[int, date] = {}\\n\\n    for d in sim_dates:\\n        # Thời gian khởi hành HN\\n        dep_base = datetime(d.year, d.month, d.day, 22, 20)\\n\\n        trip = {\\n            \\\"id\\\": trip_id,\\n            \\\"train_id\\\": 1,\\n            \\\"service_date\\\": d.isoformat(),\\n            \\\"origin_station_id\\\": STATIONS[0][\\\"id\\\"],\\n            \\\"destination_station_id\\\": STATIONS[-1][\\\"id\\\"],\\n            \\\"departure_at\\\": dep_base.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n            \\\"arrival_at\\\": (dep_base + timedelta(hours=31 + 25/60)).strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n            \\\"status\\\": \\\"completed\\\" if d \u003c date.today() else \\\"scheduled\\\",\\n            \\\"created_at\\\": dep_base.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n            \\\"updated_at\\\": dep_base.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n        }\\n        trips.append(trip)\\n        trip_date_map[trip_id] = d\\n        trip_segment_map[trip_id] = {}\\n\\n        # Segments (19 chặng liên tiếp)\\n        for seq in range(len(STATIONS) - 1):\\n            s_from = STATIONS[seq]\\n            s_to   = STATIONS[seq + 1]\\n            dist   = float(s_to[\\\"km\\\"] - s_from[\\\"km\\\"])\\n            dep_offset = STATION_HOUR_OFFSET[s_from[\\\"code\\\"]]\\n            arr_offset = STATION_HOUR_OFFSET[s_to[\\\"code\\\"]]\\n            dep_at = dep_base + timedelta(hours=dep_offset)\\n            arr_at = dep_base + timedelta(hours=arr_offset)\\n\\n            seg = {\\n                \\\"id\\\": segment_id,\\n                \\\"trip_id\\\": trip_id,\\n                \\\"sequence_no\\\": seq + 1,\\n                \\\"origin_station_id\\\": s_from[\\\"id\\\"],\\n                \\\"destination_station_id\\\": s_to[\\\"id\\\"],\\n                \\\"departure_at\\\": dep_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                \\\"arrival_at\\\": arr_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                \\\"distance_km\\\": dist,\\n                \\\"created_at\\\": dep_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n            }\\n            segments_all.append(seg)\\n            trip_segment_map[trip_id][seq + 1] = segment_id  # seq_no -\u003e seg_id\\n\\n            # Capacities per seat_type\\n            for st in SEAT_TYPES:\\n                seg_capacities.append({\\n                    \\\"segment_id\\\": segment_id,\\n                    \\\"seat_type\\\": st[\\\"code\\\"],\\n                    \\\"capacity\\\": st[\\\"capacity_per_trip\\\"],\\n                    \\\"created_at\\\": dep_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                    \\\"updated_at\\\": dep_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                })\\n                seg_inventory.append({\\n                    \\\"segment_id\\\": segment_id,\\n                    \\\"seat_type\\\": st[\\\"code\\\"],\\n                    \\\"remaining\\\": st[\\\"capacity_per_trip\\\"],\\n                    \\\"updated_at\\\": dep_at.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                })\\n\\n            segment_id += 1\\n\\n        # Seats (444 chỗ/chuyến)\\n        for st in SEAT_TYPES:\\n            cfg = SEAT_CONFIGS[st[\\\"code\\\"]]\\n            for coach_no in range(1, cfg[\\\"coaches\\\"] + 1):\\n                for seat_no in range(1, cfg[\\\"per_coach\\\"] + 1):\\n                    seats_all.append({\\n                        \\\"id\\\": seat_id,\\n                        \\\"trip_id\\\": trip_id,\\n                        \\\"coach_no\\\": f\\\"{coach_no:02d}\\\",\\n                        \\\"seat_no\\\": f\\\"{seat_no:02d}\\\",\\n                        \\\"seat_type\\\": st[\\\"code\\\"],\\n                        \\\"status\\\": \\\"available\\\",\\n                        \\\"created_at\\\": dep_base.strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S+07:00\\\"),\\n                    })\\n                    seat_id += 1\\n\\n        trip_id += 1\\n\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"trips.csv\\\", trips)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"segments.csv\\\", segments_all)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"seats.csv\\\", seats_all)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"segment_capacities.csv\\\", seg_capacities)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"segment_inventory.csv\\\", seg_inventory)\\n    print(f\\\"   trips={len(trips)}, segments={len(segments_all)}, seats={len(seats_all)}\\\")\\n\\n    # Build segment lookup: trip_id -\u003e list of (seq_no, seg_id, from_id, to_id)\\n    seg_by_trip: Dict[int, List[Tuple[int,int,int,int]]] = {}\\n    for seg in segments_all:\\n        tid = seg[\\\"trip_id\\\"]\\n        if tid not in seg_by_trip:\\n            seg_by_trip[tid] = []\\n        seg_by_trip[tid].append((\\n            seg[\\\"sequence_no\\\"],\\n            seg[\\\"id\\\"],\\n            seg[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"],\\n            seg[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"],\\n        ))\\n\\n    # ── Phase 4: OD Products ─────────────────\\n    print(\\\"[4/6] OD Products...\\\")\\n\\n    # Tính OD cho trip đầu tiên làm mẫu (tất cả trip cùng cấu trúc)\\n    # OD: tất cả cặp (i, j) với i \u003c j trong danh sách 20 ga theo thứ tự\\n    od_template = []   # dict {origin_idx, dest_idx, origin_id, dest_id, distance_km, seat_type, ...}\\n\\n    for i in range(len(STATIONS)):\\n        for j in range(i + 2, len(STATIONS)):  # bỏ qua chặng kề nhau (đã có segment)\\n            # Cho phép OD kề nhau cũng được, bao gồm i+1\\n            pass\\n\\n    for i in range(len(STATIONS)):\\n        for j in range(i + 1, len(STATIONS)):\\n            s_from = STATIONS[i]\\n            s_to   = STATIONS[j]\\n            dist   = float(s_to[\\\"km\\\"] - s_from[\\\"km\\\"])\\n\\n            # Segment indices mà OD này đi qua (seq_no từ i+1 đến j)\\n            seg_seqs = list(range(i + 1, j + 1))  # seq_no trong trip\\n\\n            # Kiểm tra có qua chặng Huế–Đà Nẵng không (seq=9, vì Huế là station[8], ĐN là station[9])\\n            # Huế là STATIONS[8] (id=9), ĐN là STATIONS[9] (id=10)\\n            # Segment Huế→ĐN là seq_no = 9 (i=8 → seq=9)\\n            BOTTLENECK_SEQ = 9  # STATIONS[8]→STATIONS[9]\\n            traverses_bottleneck = BOTTLENECK_SEQ in seg_seqs\\n\\n            for st in SEAT_TYPES:\\n                od_template.append({\\n                    \\\"origin_idx\\\": i,\\n                    \\\"dest_idx\\\": j,\\n                    \\\"origin_station_id\\\": s_from[\\\"id\\\"],\\n                    \\\"destination_station_id\\\": s_to[\\\"id\\\"],\\n                    \\\"distance_km\\\": dist,\\n                    \\\"seat_type\\\": st[\\\"code\\\"],\\n                    \\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\": traverses_bottleneck,\\n                    \\\"segment_seqs\\\": seg_seqs,\\n                    \\\"fare_class\\\": \\\"standard\\\",\\n                })\\n\\n    # Calibrate K với danh sách OD template\\n    print(\\\"   Calibrating K...\\\")\\n    od_for_calib = [{\\n        \\\"origin_station_id\\\": od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"],\\n        \\\"destination_station_id\\\": od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"],\\n        \\\"seat_type\\\": od[\\\"seat_type\\\"],\\n        \\\"distance_km\\\": od[\\\"distance_km\\\"],\\n        \\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\": od[\\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\"],\\n        \\\"segment_indices\\\": od[\\\"segment_seqs\\\"],\\n    } for od in od_template]\\n    K = calibrate_K(od_for_calib, target_load=0.65)\\n    # Điều chỉnh K cho nút cổ chai (tải ~0.80 ngày thường)\\n    print(f\\\"   K = {K:.4f}\\\")\\n\\n    # Lọc OD: ≥1 đầu là hub HOẶC base_od ≥ 0.5 khách/ngày (K=đã calib)\\n    def _base_od_k1(od: dict) -\u003e float:\\n        origin = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"]]\\n        dest   = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"]]\\n        return (origin[\\\"pop\\\"] * dest[\\\"pop\\\"]\\n                * math.exp(-od[\\\"distance_km\\\"] / 800)\\n                * pair_boost(od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"], od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"], od[\\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\"])\\n                * seat_share(od[\\\"distance_km\\\"], od[\\\"seat_type\\\"]))\\n\\n    THRESHOLD_BASE_OD = 0.5 / K if K \u003e 0 else 0.001\\n\\n    active_od_template = []\\n    for od in od_template:\\n        has_hub = (od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"] in HUB_IDS or\\n                   od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"] in HUB_IDS)\\n        base = _base_od_k1(od)\\n        if has_hub or base \u003e= THRESHOLD_BASE_OD:\\n            active_od_template.append(od)\\n\\n    print(f\\\"   Active OD templates (per trip): {len(active_od_template)} / {len(od_template)}\\\")\\n\\n    # Sinh od_products + od_product_segments cho tất cả trips\\n    od_products = []\\n    od_product_segments = []\\n    od_product_id = 1\\n\\n    # Map: trip_id -\u003e {(origin_id, dest_id, seat_type) -\u003e od_product_id}\\n    trip_od_map: Dict[int, Dict[Tuple, int]] = {}\\n\\n    for trip in trips:\\n        tid = trip[\\\"id\\\"]\\n        trip_od_map[tid] = {}\\n        seg_map = trip_segment_map[tid]  # seq_no -\u003e seg_id\\n        dep_base = trip[\\\"departure_at\\\"]\\n\\n        for od in active_od_template:\\n            bp = base_price(od[\\\"seat_type\\\"], od[\\\"distance_km\\\"])\\n            odp = {\\n                \\\"id\\\": od_product_id,\\n                \\\"trip_id\\\": tid,\\n                \\\"origin_station_id\\\": od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"],\\n                \\\"destination_station_id\\\": od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"],\\n                \\\"seat_type\\\": od[\\\"seat_type\\\"],\\n                \\\"fare_class\\\": od[\\\"fare_class\\\"],\\n                \\\"base_price\\\": bp,\\n                \\\"distance_km\\\": od[\\\"distance_km\\\"],\\n                \\\"is_active\\\": True,\\n                \\\"created_at\\\": dep_base,\\n                \\\"updated_at\\\": dep_base,\\n            }\\n            od_products.append(odp)\\n\\n            key = (od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"], od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"], od[\\\"seat_type\\\"])\\n            trip_od_map[tid][key] = od_product_id\\n\\n            # OD product segments\\n            for seq in od[\\\"segment_seqs\\\"]:\\n                seg_id = seg_map.get(seq)\\n                if seg_id:\\n                    od_product_segments.append({\\n                        \\\"od_product_id\\\": od_product_id,\\n                        \\\"segment_id\\\": seg_id,\\n                    })\\n\\n            od_product_id += 1\\n\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"od_products.csv\\\", od_products)\\n    _write_csv(SEEDS_DIR, \\\"od_product_segments.csv\\\", od_product_segments)\\n    print(f\\\"   od_products={len(od_products)}, od_product_segments={len(od_product_segments)}\\\")\\n\\n    # ── Phase 5: Simulation ──────────────────\\n    print(\\\"[5/6] Simulation (demand → bookings → search_logs)...\\\")\\n\\n    bookings = []\\n    search_logs = []\\n    ground_truth_rows = []\\n\\n    booking_id = 1\\n    search_log_id = 1\\n\\n    # Inventory theo (trip_id, segment_seq, seat_type) → remaining\\n    # Khởi tạo từ capacity\\n    inventory: Dict[Tuple[int,int,str], int] = {}\\n    for trip in trips:\\n        tid = trip[\\\"id\\\"]\\n        for seq in range(1, 20):  # 19 chặng\\n            for st in SEAT_TYPES:\\n                inventory[(tid, seq, st[\\\"code\\\"])] = st[\\\"capacity_per_trip\\\"]\\n\\n    # Seat assignment pool: trip_id -\u003e seat_type -\u003e list of seat_id (available)\\n    seat_pool: Dict[Tuple[int,str], List[int]] = {}\\n    for seat in seats_all:\\n        key = (seat[\\\"trip_id\\\"], seat[\\\"seat_type\\\"])\\n        if key not in seat_pool:\\n            seat_pool[key] = []\\n        seat_pool[key].append(seat[\\\"id\\\"])\\n\\n    n_trips = len(trips)\\n    for trip_idx, trip in enumerate(trips):\\n        if trip_idx % 100 == 0:\\n            print(f\\\"   Simulating trip {trip_idx+1}/{n_trips}...\\\", end=\\\"\\\\r\\\")\\n\\n        tid = trip[\\\"id\\\"]\\n        service_date = date.fromisoformat(trip[\\\"service_date\\\"])\\n        seg_map = trip_segment_map[tid]  # seq_no -\u003e seg_id\\n\\n        for od in active_od_template:\\n            origin = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"]]\\n            dest   = STATION_BY_ID[od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"]]\\n            seat_type = od[\\\"seat_type\\\"]\\n            dist   = od[\\\"distance_km\\\"]\\n            traverses = od[\\\"traverses_bottleneck\\\"]\\n            bp = base_price(seat_type, dist)\\n\\n            lam = compute_lambda(origin, dest, dist, seat_type, traverses, service_date, K)\\n            D = sample_demand(lam)\\n\\n            # Ground truth record\\n            gt_row = {\\n                \\\"trip_id\\\": tid,\\n                \\\"service_date\\\": service_date.isoformat(),\\n                \\\"origin_station_id\\\": od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"],\\n                \\\"destination_station_id\\\": od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"],\\n                \\\"seat_type\\\": seat_type,\\n                \\\"lambda_true\\\": round(lam, 4),\\n                \\\"demand_uncensored\\\": D,\\n                \\\"wtp_median\\\": int(round(WTP_MEDIAN_RATIO * bp)),\\n                \\\"wtp_sigma\\\": WTP_SIGMA,\\n                \\\"base_price\\\": bp,\\n            }\\n            ground_truth_rows.append(gt_row)\\n\\n            if D == 0:\\n                continue\\n\\n            # Trải D qua booking window\\n            weights = booking_curve_weights(BOOKING_WINDOW, service_date)\\n            # Phân bổ số khách theo weights (multinomial)\\n            arrivals_per_day = rng.multinomial(D, weights)\\n            # arrivals_per_day[0] = 60 ngày trước, [59] = 1 ngày trước\\n\\n            od_key = (od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"], od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"], seat_type)\\n            od_product_id_cur = trip_od_map[tid].get(od_key)\\n\\n            for t_idx, n_arrivals in enumerate(arrivals_per_day):\\n                lead_days = BOOKING_WINDOW - t_idx  # ngày trước chuyến\\n                book_date = service_date - timedelta(days=lead_days)\\n                if book_date \u003c SIM_START:\\n                    continue\\n\\n                weekday = book_date.weekday()\\n                disp_price = displayed_price(bp, lead_days, weekday, rng)\\n\\n                for _ in range(n_arrivals):\\n                    # Check tồn kho trên MỌI chặng OD đi qua\\n                    can_book = all(\\n                        inventory.get((tid, seq, seat_type), 0) \u003e 0\\n                        for seq in od[\\\"segment_seqs\\\"]\\n                    )\\n\\n                    if not can_book:\\n                        # Hết chỗ → sold_out\\n                        search_logs.append({\\n                            \\\"id\\\": search_log_id,\\n                            \\\"searched_at\\\": book_date.isoformat() + \\\"T12:00:00+07:00\\\",\\n                            \\\"origin_station_id\\\": od[\\\"origin_station_id\\\"],\\n                            \\\"destination_station_id\\\": od[\\\"destination_station_id\\\"],\\n                            \\\"seat_type\\\": seat_type,\\n                            \\\"service_date\\\": service_date.isoformat(),\\n                            \\\"result\\\": \\\"sold_out\\\",\\n                            \\\"od_product_id\\\": od_product_id_cur,\\n                            \\\"channel\\\": \\\"web\\\",\\n                            \\\"created_at\\\": book_date.isoformat() + \\\"T12:00:00+07:00\\\",\\n                        })\\n                        search_log_id += 1\\n                        continue\\n\\n                    # Sinh WTP\\n                    mu_log = math.log(WTP_MEDIAN_RATIO * bp)\\n                    wtp = rng.lognormal(mu_log, WTP_SIGMA)\\n\\n                    if wtp \u003e= disp_price:\\n                        # Mua được\\n                        # Gán ghế\\n                        seat_key = (tid, seat_type)\\n                        pool = seat_pool.get(seat_key, [])\\n          